    <summary>NetRadio plays internet radio streams and manages your favorite stations.</summary>
    <description>Netradio plays Internet live streams from radio stations and offers simple management for up to 24 stations.

The application includes a search function for new stations. It uses the API from www.radio-browser.info for this.

Live stream URLs of your favourite stations are therefore automatically transferred.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>### New in version 2.5

- Automatic stream title update/synchronization
- Now 25 buttons on player page
- Optimized online search to find internet radios
- The listened stream can be recorded in a file
- m3u8-Support (HLS playlists)
- History of played songs, export possible
- MiniPlayer or minimize to tray
- Scheduled tasks (play, record, stop)
- Portable version
    </releaseNotes>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency id="dotnet-8.0-desktopruntime" />
    </dependencies>
